blog.description: Hi, I’m Vee! Boston, MA. Born in 1989 in Pennsylvania and found my happily ever after with a British man—oh, and I have three cats. Just like Taylor Swift 💖 (Insta + Twitter: @veeswift13)

summary: Hi! 👋🏻 So, I just want to take a second to introduce myself since I’m new to Instagram + Tumblr, and I’ve been adding literally...
body: Hi! 👋🏻 So, I just want to take a second to introduce myself since I’m new to Instagram + Tumblr, and I’ve been adding literally every Swiftie I can find on here since joining a day ago.😝 My name is Vee, and I live in Boston, MA. ☺️ Like @taylorswift, I’m 29 years old, I’m originally from Pennsylvania, and my husband is British 💜 I was a casual Swiftie until 2015 when I went to my first Taylor Swift concert. Seeing Taylor perform live was honestly the most magical thing I’ve experienced, and if you’ve been to a Taylor Swift concert, I know I don’t even need to explain why that is. (See if you can guess which TS lyric I’m dressed as in this picture!) Taylor puts her heart and soul into absolutely every single performance. Everything she does is crafted with the utmost care and precision. Y’all know I’m including #TS7 into that mix! I’m so happy to be part of this fandom, and I hope we’re wrong about literally every #ts7theory.. just so Taylor can post on April 26 and we can all go bald because our wigs will have flown into orbit. Bald Swifties for life. 💜😂 Please feel free to add me or message me (Insta: veeswift13)! I’ll always follow back and would love to talk to you guys! ☺️☺️💜🌈💫☁️⭐️💎
